            noted however, that your character doesn’t need to reflect the title of their identity and players can even come up with their own names to use over the default ones.
            For example, if a player wants to make a character that’s background is that of a spy, but they want the bonuses that the Larcenist identity gives, their identity
            can be: Spy (Larcenist).This doesn’t interfere with the actual mechanics of identities, so players are encouraged to do whatever suits their character’s story!
        </p>

